msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA_LOREDROP\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"好了，这样应该就行了！出发前，我会帮你整理好装备。虚伪辉光的追随者们——更不用"
