#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:266
msgid "data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/text"
msgstr "突然，你的飞船从虫洞的另一端被抛射出来——但并未完全失去动力。它继续向前飞驰，"
"而就在这时……一切都开始变得模糊。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:271
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "握紧你的手，摇了摇头。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:273
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你开始紧紧攥住……你意识到，是幽影。当你慌忙想要抓住什么东西时，它一定是离你最"
"近的存在。你的手抓着它那奇异的金属表面，仿佛正在渐渐失去知觉……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:275
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "猛地将手从幽影上抽离。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:277
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"即便你猛地抽回手，却只感觉手掌愈发麻木。的确，一切都变得如此……模糊不清。你的"
"视觉、触觉、嗅觉——就连思考能力也在不断衰退。你绝望地踉跄了一下，笨拙地跌落在"
"地。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:279
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "发生……什么事了……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:281
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "在你所有感官消散之前，最后看到的，是那具幽影——静静伫立在你身前，一如往常般死"
"寂。随后，一切都陷入……黑暗……并且……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:283
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
