#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:301
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "如果你能听见我……那就试着想象出形状。物体，实体——我想，这些都是光裔族在这里留"
"下的全部东西了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:303
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一个尖叫、痛苦、饱受折磨的灵魂——那是所有逝去一切的总和。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:305
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"哦，天啊——好吧！至少你能听见我说话，可是……我需要你稍微放松一点。我自己……也很"
"害怕。我不知道我在哪里，而且……我……我想你也不比我更清楚，对吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:307
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "想象一片浑浊的湖——湖中的一切对它自身与任何旁观者而言都是谜。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:311
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "想象一片清澈见底的湖——湖中的一切清晰可见，且早已被洞悉。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:313
msgid ""
