"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"好吧，一边是碎灵族，另一边则是……呃……烬灵族？没错，看来是这样。鉴于你的飞船对"
"光裔族来说无法生存，它们俩对你都构不成太大威胁……如果你想解决这件事，你真正要"
"做的，就是把其中一方引诱到飞船上。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1577
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[@req=\"DDFALSERADIANCE_RADIANT_CORE_TIERONE_BREAKLING\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一枚碎灵族辉光核心——它就在附近。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1579
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[@req=\"DDFALSERADIANCE_RADIANT_CORE_TIERONE_BREAKLING\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这……真是个有意思的想法。或许不用把它们引诱到飞船上，你可以用你的辉光核心把碎"
"灵族引开？这样一来，烬灵族就能使用这里的空间，而碎灵族也能在别处拥有属于它们"
"自己的地盘！不错，呃……真是个好主意，我！我觉得……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1581
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[@req=\"DDFALSERADIANCE_RADIANT_CORE_TIERONE_BREAKLING\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一个更遥远的地方——那是光的归宿。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1587
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[@req=\"DDFALSERADIANCE_RADIANT_CORE_TIERONE_CINDERLING\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一枚烬灵族辉光核心——它就在附近。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1589
