#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2020
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……多么惨烈的景象。成百上千，甚至数以千计死去的光裔族——每一具都在宇宙中漫无目"
"的地飘荡……在我姐姐担任他们监管者的漫长岁月里，她从未见过如此大规模的葬身之地"
"。虽然我很不愿这么说，但我……我认为这虚伪辉光干的。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2022
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象残酷——其行径卑劣至极。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2024
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"是啊，就算是他们，这也实在太卑劣了……我无法想象他们为什么觉得有必要做这种事。"
"我压根就没法假装理解他们的想法，可是……这场……这场……这场屠杀，跟他们追求神性又"
"有什么关系？他们尽可以去与其他光裔族为敌，但说到底，这难道不恰恰证明了，真正"
"毫无理智的是他们自己吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2026
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象暴政——其魔爪伸向多元宇宙的每一个角落。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2028
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "在你的世界里，也有……也有像虚伪辉光这样的人吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2030
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一个例证——那场叛乱，方方面面都卑劣至极。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2032
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这……不知为何，听起来很熟悉。我也不太清楚为什么，但是……不管怎样，我，啊……我真"
"的迫不及待想等我姐姐醒来，让一切恢复正常。我不忍心看到光裔族遭受这样的苦难，"
"毕竟他们一开始已经付出了那么多才逃离痛苦……他们牺牲的意义——他们立下的誓言——不"
"就是为了避免这样的纷争吗？如果虚伪辉光能轻而易举地将这一切夺走，那这一切又都"
"是为了什么……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2034
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象寂静——为逝者而生的肃穆时刻。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2036
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……对了，说到……呃……光裔族……我们不能就这么把他们丢下。他们的生死轮回通常是被汇"
"聚融合，再以新的形态转世，但……如今掘墓者被虚伪辉光控制，它的职责似乎也就此搁"
"置了。不过……我姐姐还是会尽力代它完成！即便她的载体如今这般状态，她对光裔族依"
"然拥有极强的影响力——你只需要在心中构想你希望他们呈现的样子，剩下的交给她就好"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2038
