msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr "……噢，天父啊，那是一只巨大的光裔族。而且，它……没错，就是它！它居然在吞噬这里"
"的虚伪辉光侦察兵——干得好，大家伙！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2479
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一声欢呼——庆祝邪恶的覆灭。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2481
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"看到光裔族奋起反抗创世装置带来的腐化，实在令人振奋。即便我姐姐处于现在这种状"
"态，它们依然在顽强支撑……不仅如此，啊，这一只看起来还愈发强盛！她从未见过光裔"
"族变得如此巨大——呃，我想主要是因为光裔族通常不会内斗、互相吞噬吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2483
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一份献礼——以伟大之名献上的崇敬。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2485
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你……觉得你能喂它吗？我，啊……我看没什么不行，就算这有点奇怪。说不定它反过来也"
"能帮到你？我是说，除了它已经做到的——呃……减缓虚伪辉光的推进之外。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2487
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "想象一份微薄之物——微小，却无比诚挚。[20~]"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2489
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"噢，哇——它居然就，呃……直接吸收杂物是吧？看来你给的这点东西根本不够，它还饿着…"
"…不过……我觉得这说不定是件好事？你把它的胃口吊起来了，对虚伪辉光来说，它只会变"
"成一个更大的麻烦。谢……谢谢你，光裔族先生！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2497
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "想象一次援手——分量寻常却恰到好处。 [40~]"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2499
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"哦，哇——它居然真的……吸收杂物是吧？至少从它震动的样子来看，它好像还挺受用的。"
"还是说，呃……它在分裂？等等，没错——它绝对是在分裂。有点恶心，但，啊……谢……谢谢"
"你，光裔族先生！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2507
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "想象一盘盛馔——配得上如此璀璨的生命。[80~]"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2509
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"哦，哇——它居然真的，呃……吸收杂物是吧？即便如此，它散发的光芒依旧如此美丽……这"
"就是被赐福的感觉吗？如此璀璨夺目，甚至能与虚伪辉光相抗衡……如果你有其他光裔族"
"，它们应该会因这样一个希望象征的存在而稍稍安定。谢……谢谢你，了不起的光裔族先"
"生！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2518
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "想象一片虚空——空无一物，却并非没有意志。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2520
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_THEDEVOURER\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"好吧，就算你没什么能给它的，我相信这位大家伙也会领这份心意的！而且，它看起来"
"已经要离开了。它要走我还挺舍不得的，不过……或许我们某天还会再遇见它？或者，呃…"
"…至少我姐姐可能会——到时候，她就能告诉我们它一切都好！"

